### User Profile & Notifications API Tests
# Set the userToken

@baseUrl = http://localhost:10000/api
@userToken = your_user_jwt_token_here

###
# 1. Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###
# 2. Update User Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "phoneNumber": "1234567890"
}

###
# 3. Update User Profile Picture (Requires multipart/form-data via Rest Client)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=ProfilePictureBoundary

--ProfilePictureBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="profilePicture"; filename="avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./avatar.png
--ProfilePictureBoundary--

###
# 4. Get User Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
